          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". It signifies properly persons without yoke, vile and wretched miscreants, lawless and rebellious, that will suffer no restraint, that neither fear God nor reverence man. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
