            "text": "",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "bld",
        "text": "From among you, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " i.e. from your church and religion. It notes a separation or departure from them, not in place, (as appears by their partnership with their fellow citizens both in the sin and punishment, as it here follows,) but in heart, doctrine, and worship, as the same phrase is used, ",
        "children": []
